%mysql
INSERT INTO mdt_poc.tr_stats VALUES 
((SELECT runid FROM mdt_poc.parameters),(SELECT uovid FROM mdt_poc.parameters), 'iptable_1_2', 'optable_1_2_p', (SELECT 
       CASE WHEN ((select count(*) from mdt_poc.optable_1_2_p)=(select count(*) from mdt_poc.optable_1_2_t) AND (select count(*) from mdt_poc.optable_1_2_p) = (select count(*) from mdt_poc.optable_1_2_p A inner join  mdt_poc.optable_1_2_t B ON A.city = B.city AND A.count = B.count))
       THEN 'SUCCESS'
       ELSE 'FAILURE'
       END AS RowCountResult), 'desc', NOW());
